2020年12月30日，一架载有新成立的也门聯合政府成员的飞机降落在[[也门|也门]]西南部的[[亚丁国际机场|亚丁国际机场]]。当乘客下机时，机场響起了爆炸声和枪声，此次襲擊造成至少26人死亡<ref>{{Cite web |title=葉門亞丁機場遇襲增至26死 傷亡恐再增加 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012310012.aspx |accessdate=2021-01-01 |author=楊昭彥 |date=2020-12-30 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |location=亞丁 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112134602/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012310012.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，110人受伤<ref name="Mukhashaf">{{Cite news|author=Mukhashaf|first=Mohammed|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security/blast-gunfire-at-aden-airport-after-plane-carrying-new-government-lands-5-killed-idUSKBN29413E?il=0|title=Twenty-two killed in attack on Aden airport after new Yemen cabinet lands|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107161612/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security/blast-gunfire-at-aden-airport-after-plane-carrying-new-government-lands-5-killed-idUSKBN29413E?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|McKernan}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=也门新政府官员甫返国 机场猛烈爆炸至少16死60伤|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2402221.html|accessdate=2021-01-01|date=2020-12-30|work=www.sinchew.com.my|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230144831/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2402221.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過此次襲擊並未造成机上乘客受伤。襲擊發生後，也门新聯合政府成员迅速前往也門總統府马什克宫躲避{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy}}。

== 背景 ==
[[也门内战_(2014年至今)|也門内战]]爆發後，胡塞武裝控制也門首都[[萨那|萨那]]，也门政府被迫驻扎在临时首都[[亚丁|亚丁]]。2019年，[[南方过渡委员会|南方过渡委员会]]攻占亚丁并迫使也門政府流亡至沙特阿拉伯<ref name="bbc">{{Cite news|title=Yemen war: Deadly attack at Aden airport as new government arrives|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-55484436|date=2020-12-31|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230114446/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-55484436|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Al-Batati&Yee">{{cite news|last1=Al-Batati|first1=Saeed|last2=Yee|first2=Vivian|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/30/world/middleeast/yemen-explosion-airport.html|title=Yemen Airport Is Attacked as New Government Arrives|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2020-12-30|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230131846/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/30/world/middleeast/yemen-explosion-airport.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|npr}} 。

2020年12月，也门政府与[[南方過渡委員會|南方過渡委員會]]在[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]的調解下组建了聯合政府<ref name="jazeera">{{Cite web|title=Blasts hit Yemen's Aden airport as new unity government arrives|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/30/blasts-at-yemens-aden-airport-as-new-unity-government-arrives|accessdate=2020-12-31|date=2020-12-30|publisher=Al Jazeera English|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230112754/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/30/blasts-at-yemens-aden-airport-as-new-unity-government-arrives|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|bbc}}。沙特調解的目的是结束内斗，以便双方能够在[[也门内战_(2014年至今)|也門内战]]中共同打击[[胡塞武裝|胡塞武裝]]{{R|jazeera|npr|arabnews}}。2020年12月26日，由[[也门总理|也门总理]][[迈茵·阿卜杜勒马利克·赛义德|迈茵·阿卜杜勒马利克·赛义德]]领导的新聯合政府在[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]首都[[利雅得|利雅得]]宣誓就职<ref name="cabinet.jazeera">{{Cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/26/yemens-new-government-sworn-in-after-power-sharing-agreement|title=New Yemen gov't sworn in after Saudi-brokered power-sharing deal|publisher=Al Jazeera English|date=2020-12-26|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226164527/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/26/yemens-new-government-sworn-in-after-power-sharing-agreement|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cabinet.arabnews">{{Cite news|author=Al-Batati|first=Saeed|url=https://arab.news/2zdkh|title=Yemen's new government sworn in, ending months of wrangling|date=2020-12-26|work=Arab News|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226183128/https://arab.news/2zdkh|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 襲擊 ==
2020年12月30日，一架也门飞机从沙特阿拉伯飞往也门西南部港口城市亚丁，机上载有包括总理在内的新成立的也门聯合政府成员以及沙特驻也门大使{{R|McKernan|Al-Mujahed&Raghavan}}{{Efn|President Hadi, who has been living in Riyadh after the Houthi rebels took control of Sanaa, was not aboard.{{r|jazeera|npr}}}}。机场大厅里挤满了迎接新聯合政府成员的也門官员以及平民<ref name="arabnews">{{Cite news|author=Al-Batati|first=Saeed|url=https://www.arabnews.com/node/1784946/middle-east|title=27 dead, dozens wounded in deadly attack on Aden airport|work=Arab News|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231072232/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1784946/middle-east|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外還有数百人聚集在[[停機坪|停机坪]]上{{R|npr}}。当飛機上乘客下机时，巨大的爆炸声響起<ref name="McKernan">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/30/aden-airport-blasts-kill-16-in-attack-directed-at-yemen-government|title=Aden airport blasts kill 26 in attack 'directed at Yemen government'|first=Bethan|author=McKernan|date=2020-12-30|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101230840/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/30/aden-airport-blasts-kill-16-in-attack-directed-at-yemen-government|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=也门新政府官员返国 机场猛烈爆炸至少5死|url=https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20201230/也门新政府官员返国-机场猛烈爆炸至少5死/|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2021-01-01|work=光华网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128112831/https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20201230/%e4%b9%9f%e9%97%a8%e6%96%b0%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e5%ae%98%e5%91%98%e8%bf%94%e5%9b%bd-%e6%9c%ba%e5%9c%ba%e7%8c%9b%e7%83%88%e7%88%86%e7%82%b8%e8%87%b3%e5%b0%915%e6%ad%bb/}}</ref>{{Efn|There are conflicting reports regarding how many explosions there were, with reports ranging from two to four.{{r|Al-Haj&Magdy|bbc}}}}。

爆炸声響起後，数百名群众四處奔散，已經下飞机的聯合政府部长们有的跑回飞机，有的四處寻找掩体{{R|npr}}<ref name="cbc">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/yemen-airport-explosion-1.5857199|title=Yemeni officials say blast at Aden airport kills 25, wounds 110|work=CBC News|agency=Associated Press|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101222022/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/yemen-airport-explosion-1.5857199|dead-url=no}}</ref>。袭击发生后，人们看到躺在停机坪和机场其他地方的尸体，机场候机楼冒出浓浓的烟雾{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy|Mukhashaf|McKernan}}。

襲擊造成至少26人死亡，110人受伤，其中33人伤势严重{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy}}<ref name="Al-Mujahed&Raghavan">{{Cite news|author=Al-Mujahed|first=Ali|author2=Raghavan|first2=Sudarsan|url=https://washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/aden-explosion-airport-yemen/2020/12/30/06077e2a-4a9f-11eb-97b6-4eb9f72ff46b_story.html|title=Explosions rock Aden airport, killing at least 22, as new Yemen government arrives|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231114528/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/aden-explosion-airport-yemen/2020/12/30/06077e2a-4a9f-11eb-97b6-4eb9f72ff46b_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遇難者中包括[[红十字国际委员会|红十字国际委员会]]的3名成员（2名也门人和1名[[卢旺达|卢旺达人]]）<ref name="npr">{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/12/30/951419361/explosion-rocks-yemeni-airport-where-new-government-just-landed|title=Deadly Explosion Rocks Yemeni Airport Just As New Government Members Land|publisher=[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230172345/https://www.npr.org/2020/12/30/951419361/explosion-rocks-yemeni-airport-where-new-government-just-landed|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="icrc">{{Cite press release|url=https://www.icrc.org/en/document/yemen-2-icrc-staff-members-killed-1-unaccounted-after-airport-blast|title=Yemen: 3 ICRC staff members killed in airport blast|date=2020-12-30|publisher=International Committee of the Red Cross|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231150353/https://www.icrc.org/en/document/yemen-2-icrc-staff-members-killed-1-unaccounted-after-airport-blast|dead-url=no}}</ref>、一名公共工程部副部长<ref name="Malsin&al-Batati">{{Cite news|author=Malsin|first=Jared|author2=al-Batati|first2=Saleh|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/yemen-airport-attack-kills-22-as-new-saudi-backed-government-arrives-11609349273|title=Yemen Airport Attack Kills 22 as New Saudi-Backed Government Arrives|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102024508/https://www.wsj.com/articles/yemen-airport-attack-kills-22-as-new-saudi-backed-government-arrives-11609349273|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|bbc}}{{Efn|It has also been reported that a government official referred to as "deputy minister of housing" or "undersecretary at the labour ministry" has been killed, but it is unclear if this person is the same as the deputy minister of public works.<ref name="Cheeseman">{{cite news|last=Cheeseman|first=Abbie|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/12/30/explosions-greet-new-unity-government-key-yemen-port/|title=Explosions greet new 'unity' government at key Yemen airport|work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|date=2020-12-30|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231215622/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/12/30/explosions-greet-new-unity-government-key-yemen-port/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{r|bbc}} ''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'', however, stated that it was the deputy transport minister who was reported dead.{{r|Al-Batati&Yee}}}}以及一名也门电视新闻频道{{link-en|Belqees TV}}的记者<ref name="9news">{{Cite web|title=Explosions and gunfire rock airport in Yemen|url=https://www.9news.com.au/videos/world/explosions-and-gunfire-rock-airport-in-yemen/ckjcj7vnt00610hqwewoolfqw|accessdate=2020-12-31|date=2020-12-31|work=[[Ninemsn|Ninemsn]]|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231085436/https://www.9news.com.au/videos/world/explosions-and-gunfire-rock-airport-in-yemen/ckjcj7vnt00610hqwewoolfqw|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy}}。所有伤亡人員都位於候机楼内{{R|arabnews|Cheeseman}}<ref name="Spencer">{{Cite news|author=Spencer|first=Richard|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/airport-explosions-target-yemens-new-government-rbbvj3jvb|title=Attack on Yemen airport kills 25|work=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124090059/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/airport-explosions-target-yemens-new-government-rbbvj3jvb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。飞机上的所有乘客均未受伤{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy}}。新聯合政府成員以及沙特大使迅速被送往亚丁的总统府马什克宫以确保安全{{R|jazeera|Al-Haj&Magdy}} 。

== 後續 ==
也门外交部长{{link-en|艾哈迈德·阿瓦德·本·穆巴拉克|Ahmad Awad bin Mubarak}}最初将这次袭击归咎于胡塞武装，并称胡塞武装向机场发射了4枚弹道导弹，但其在发表声明时没有提供证据，胡塞武装也否认对此次襲擊负责<ref name="Al-Haj&Magdy">{{Cite news|author=Al-Haj|first=Ahmed|author2=Magdy|first2=Samy|date=2020-12-30|title=Yemeni officials: Blast at Aden airport kills 25, wounds 110|publisher=[[美联社|美联社]]|url=https://apnews.com/article/yemen-middle-east-cabinets-sanaa-9fdc085dab7abb0a0f9888158be5ab0d|accessdate=2020-12-30|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230124331/https://apnews.com/article/yemen-middle-east-cabinets-sanaa-9fdc085dab7abb0a0f9888158be5ab0d|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|Malsin&al-Batati}}。南部过渡委员会将责任归咎于[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]]和[[土耳其|土耳其]]，西方國家官员表示，此次襲擊很有可能是胡塞武装所为，但不排除是[[阿拉伯半岛基地组织|阿拉伯半岛基地组织]]或其他也門南部分裂主义派别所為。也門总统[[阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪|阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪]]指示军方调查此次袭击事件{{R|npr}}。

== 反应 ==
[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[安东尼奥·古特雷斯|安东尼奥·古特雷斯]]谴责了發生在[[亚丁国际机场|亚丁国际机场]]的袭击事件，并向受害者家属以及也门政府和人民表示慰问<ref name="response.guterres">{{Cite tweet|user=OSE_Yemen|title=UN Secretary-General @antonioguterres condemns the deplorable attack on #Aden airport shortly after the arrival of the newly formed Yemeni cabinet|number=1344398049687330822|date=2020-12-30}}</ref>。

包括[[埃及|埃及]]、[[约旦|约旦]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]、[[英国|英国]]和美国在內的一些[[阿拉伯国家|阿拉伯国家]]、[[伊斯蘭國家|伊斯蘭國家]]和[[西方国家|西方国家]]都对机场袭击事件表示谴责<ref name="jazeera.live">{{cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/30/several-killed-in-attack-on-yemens-aden-airport|title=Yemen's PM condemns 'treacherous, cowardly' Aden airport attack|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-30|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230143112/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/12/30/several-killed-in-attack-on-yemens-aden-airport|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{R|Al-Haj&Magdy|Al-Mujahed&Raghavan}} 。

